 永遠難登大雅之堂 抵被人睇唔起<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97b7b3d88c006807c8ce3b502b8fbe8ad1e5b46d","tid":2172663,"uid":337052,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T18:48:53.000Z","msg":"這麼快，美國的&ldquo;報應&rdquo;就來了<br />\n來源：環球時報新媒體<br />\n<br />\n2020-08-24 16:52<br />\n據美聯社報導，美聯社的一項調查發現，在獲得今年最重要的返校學習用品筆記本電腦以及其他在線學習所需的設備方面，美國各地的學校正面臨著長達數月的短缺和長時間推遲供貨。<br />\n<a href=\"https://taiwan.huanqiu.com/article/3zbLqEu1jdA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftaiwan.huanqiu.com%2Farticle%2F3zbLqEu1jdA&d=HUgUlm9NWlnA9xfyBh3SbvUUj30esm9w7dCaRgXMgeE%3D&h=6b89d3be\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://taiwan.huanqiu.com/article/3zbLqEu1jdA</a>"},{"pid":"74cacb6ab76ce9b42cdd8ba8c95088d520f26f7c","tid":2172663,"uid":157138,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"2393bc1810b3a5fca91053b5e79f9a0729b7b753","tid":2172663,"uid":337052,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T18:41:37.000Z","msg":"特朗普稱&ldquo;中美可能脫鉤&rdquo;，趙立堅做出三點回應<br />\n<img src=\"https://rs1.huanqiucdn.cn/dp/api/images/imageDir/f5642f691cbcd414a6a799772e2bace1u5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Frs1.huanqiucdn.cn%2Fdp%2Fapi%2Fimages%2FimageDir%2Ff5642f691cbcd414a6a799772e2bace1u5.jpg&h=e99d5370&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://world.huanqiu.com/article/3zbEBF4wIgG\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fworld.huanqiu.com%2Farticle%2F3zbEBF4wIgG&d=HUgUlm9NWlnA9xfyBh3SbvUUj30esm9w7dCaRgXMgeE%3D&h=ad388a1c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://world.huanqiu.com/article/3zbEBF4wIgG</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T18:49:10.000Z","msg":"中國不忍美國自取滅亡，堅決協助美國重回正軌！果然是正義之師<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1d8d9c855550cf98f83bbc3c319cbb612aafab3","tid":2172663,"uid":278168,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T18:49:49.000Z","msg":"終於唔係石頭腳，有新term"},{"pid":"195eb4121310d57c9a147